data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"Final critique pass is acceptable: the hero reads as roofing immediately, the section rhythm alternates image/service/proof/process/contact, and the copy stays within the verified facts. The generic test hook had no project test command, so I’m treating the targeted HTML/content checks as the verification for this static artifact."}

